BAUCHI (Sundiata Post) – Incumbent Governor of Bauchi State, Mohammed Abubakar, has congratulated Senator Bala Mohammed on his emergence as governor-elect in the 2019 gubernatorial election.This is contained in a statement signed by press secretary to the governor, Abubakar Al-Sadique and made available to newsmen on Monday.The statement reads:“I wish to sincerely congratulate my brother, Senator Bala (Mohammed) on this victory at the polls.“I’m glad that in spite of the tensed campaigns we had in Bauchi State, we have been been able to sail through without bloodshed.“Let me therefore invite the Governor-elect to join me in working out the process of a peaceful transition.“I sincerely thank the entire people of Bauchi State for their support to my administration and urge them to extend the same to the in-coming administration. “I also urge governor-elect to caution his supporters to be law abiding in the celebrations since the period of campaigns is now over.”Abubakar Al-Sadique, Press Secretary to His Excellency, Gov M. A. ABUBAKAR 25-03-2019